      "label": "The System",
      "title": "A system used during live patient treatment",
      "content": "iTero is used chair-side. Three phases — RX, Scan, View — feed into each other. A breakdown in one affects the whole appointment.",
      "issuesTitle": "The three phases",
      "issues": [
        "RX → define patient, procedure, case details",
        "Scan → capture a real-time 3D model",
        "View → validate before lab submission"
